text:
This was our first time visiting a northern Vietnamese cafe and never expected that it was such a hidden charms thats makes us enjoyed our meals so much!

The ambiance is great with music and the atmosphere is very comfortable, we were also amazed by their wide selection of food & beverages and their dessert display.

